
 This patch permit to disable the _FORTIFY_SOURCE flag that is
 added by some distributions.

 Apply it to version 2.4.4 with:

 cd <bacula-source>
 patch -p0 <2.4.4-fortify.patch
 ./configure <your options>
 make
 ...
 make install



